user.biography: Join the fever and explore the best nature and travel destinations with us.

node.text:
Alaskan adventures with @johnderting 💦
From 1-10, which one is your favorite?

📽 @johnderting
📍 Alaska
🎶 
1. (River sounds) - (Relaxing Radiance Music For Sleep
2, 4. Lovely - Billie Eilish and Khalid
3, 5. Rose - James Horner
6. Rainy Day - Peder B. Helland
7. The Night We Met - Lord Huron
8. What the Hell - Williams
9. Six Feet Under - Billie Eilish
10. Hymn To The Sea - Sarah Cothran & Michaila Cothran

node.text:
Umbrella tree 🌳 How impressive is this holm oak? Known as the umbrella tree. Once a year two gardeners climb up into its crown on ladders, and for two weeks they prune the tree like a skirt as they meticulously trim it into shape. Its healing powers helped James Bond recuperate – Casino Royale.

📽 @brigrc
📍Villa del Balbianello, Como, Italy
